Make Missing be nothing as Maybe String
Match Missing
  When Some Value
    Expect false is true
  When nothing
    Expect true is true

Make Present be Some "Ada" as Maybe String
Match Present
  When Some Name
    Expect Name is "Ada"
  When nothing
    Expect false is true

Make Names be List with "Ada" and "Grace"
Make Maybe First be Item 0 of Names as Maybe String
Match Maybe First
  When Some First
    Expect First is "Ada"
  When nothing
    Expect false is true

Make Inbox be New Channel of String with Capacity be 1
Send "ready" to Inbox
Make Maybe Message be Await Receive from Inbox as Maybe String
Match Maybe Message
  When Some Message
    Expect Message is "ready"
  When nothing
    Expect false is true
